    href: '/blog/future-of-ai-australian-enterprise',
    date: 'May 2026',
    readTime: '8 min read',
    author: 'All Webbed Labs Team',
  },
  {
    category: 'Mobile Development',
    title: 'Why Flutter is the Smart Choice for Enterprise Mobile App Development in 2026',
    excerpt: 'With 40% cost savings over native development and near-native performance, Flutter has become the go-to choice for enterprise mobile. Here\'s why we recommend it for most client projects.',
    href: '/blog/flutter-smart-choice-mobile-2026',
    date: 'April 2026',
    readTime: '6 min read',
    author: 'All Webbed Labs Team',
  },
  {
    category: 'Web3 & Blockchain',
